<section class="ibc-section ibc-bg-white">
    <div class="ibc-container">
        <h2 class="ibc-section-title ibc-animate">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="ibc-accent-line"></div>
        <p class="ibc-section-subtitle ibc-animate">Got questions? We've got answers. Find everything you need to know
            about our IBC tanks.</p>
        <div class="ibc-faq-list ibc-animate">
            <div class="ibc-faq-item ibc-open">
                <button class="ibc-faq-question">
                    What is an IBC tank?
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="ibc-faq-answer">
                    <p>IBC stands for Intermediate Bulk Container. It is a reusable industrial-grade container designed
                        for the storage and transport of bulk liquids and semi-solids. IBC tanks typically hold 1000
                        liters and are made from high-density polyethylene (HDPE) with a steel cage for structural
                        support. They are commonly used in agriculture, chemical storage, food processing, and
                        industrial applications across Pakistan.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ibc-faq-item">
                <button class="ibc-faq-question">
                    Can I store drinking water in an IBC tank?
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="ibc-faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes, our food-grade IBC tanks are safe for storing drinking water and other consumable liquids.
                        They are made from FDA-approved food-grade HDPE material. For regular water storage, our
                        standard water IBC tanks are also safe and widely used for rainwater harvesting and clean water
                        storage on farms and homes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ibc-faq-item">
                <button class="ibc-faq-question">
                    Do you deliver nationwide?
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="ibc-faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes, we deliver to every city, town, and rural area across Pakistan. We cover all major cities
                        including Lahore, Karachi, Islamabad, Faisalabad, Multan, Peshawar, Gujranwala, Sialkot, and
                        more. Delivery times typically range from 2-5 business days depending on your location.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ibc-faq-item">
                <button class="ibc-faq-question">
                    Are the tanks new or used?
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="ibc-faq-answer">
                    <p>We offer both new and used/refurbished IBC tanks. All our tanks undergo thorough inspection and
                        cleaning before sale. Used tanks are tested for structural integrity and chemical compatibility.
                        You can choose the option that best fits your budget and requirements.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ibc-faq-item">
                <button class="ibc-faq-question">
                    What sizes are available?
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="ibc-faq-answer">
                    <p>Our standard IBC tanks come in 1000-liter capacity, which is the most widely used size in
                        Pakistan. This size is perfect for agricultural, industrial, and commercial applications. We
                        also have smaller 500-liter options and larger custom solutions available on request.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ibc-faq-item">
                <button class="ibc-faq-question">
                    How much does delivery cost?
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="ibc-faq-answer">
                    <p>Delivery costs depend on your location and the quantity ordered. For orders within Lahore, we
                        offer free delivery on bulk orders. For other cities, we provide competitive shipping rates.
                        Contact us with your location details for an accurate delivery quote.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

